    "content": "\n<table style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" class=\"draggable toggleable-table\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th id=\"x\" style=\"text-align: right;\">Source (Hebrew)</th>\n<th style=\"text-align: left;\"><a href=\"/translate/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Contribute a translation</a></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\">\nהֲוָיַת נִשְׁמָתִי פִּתְחִי פִּי הַתִּירִי לְשׁוֹנִי וַאֲהַלֵּלֵךְ<br />\n</span></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\">\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\">\nאִמִּי<br />\nהַגִּבּוֹרָה<br />\nהַקְּדוֹשָׁה<br />\n</span></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\">\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\">\nחָנְּנִי שִׂכְלִי בְּדַעַת וּבִינָה<br />\n</span></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\">\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\">\nאַמְּצִינִי אֶל חֵיק תְּשׁוּבָתֵךְ<br />\n</span></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\">\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\">\nמַלְּאִי לִבִּי סְלִיחָה<br />\n</span></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\">\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\">\nרְאִי בְעָנְיִי, רִיבִי רִיבִי, מִמֵּיצָרִים גַּאֲלִינִי<br />\n</span></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\">\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\">\nרַפְּאִי אֶת נַפְשִׁי אֶת גּוּפִי אֶת אֲהוּבַי אֶת בְּנוֹת וּבְנֵי מִינִי<br />\n</span></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\">\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\">\nבָּרְכִי אֶת אַדְמָתֵךְ וְאֶת פִּרְיָהּ<br />\n</span></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\">\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\">\nקַבְּצִי אֵלֶיהָ אֶת נִדָּחַיִךְ בְּאַהֲבָה<br />\n</span></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\">\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\">\nהַשְׁלִיטִי מִשְׁפַּט צִדְקֵךְ<br />\nלְהַכְנִיעַ כָּל רֶשַׁע וְזָדוֹן<br />\n</span></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\">\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\">\nעִטְפִי בְּרַחֲמַיִךְ אֶת הַזַּכּוֹת וְהַצַּדִּיקוֹת<br />\nלְמַּעַן תִּשְׁכֹּנָּה עִמָּךְ בְּבֵיתֵךְ לָבֶטַח<br />\n</span></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\">\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\">\nהוֹשִׁיעִי נָא<br />\nשִׁמְעִי נָא<br />\nקַבְּלִי נָא<br />\nוְשׁוּבִי לְצִיּוֹן בְּרַחֲמִים<br />\n</span></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\">\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\">\nתּוֹדָה<br />\nשָׁלוֹם\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<hr />\n<p>This &#8220;Alternative Amida for weekday service&#8221; by הרבה דליה שחם Rabbi Dahlia Shaham, appears in <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/תפילת-האדם-סידור-רפורמי-ישראלי-101214578258569\">תפילת האדם, סידור רפורמי ישראלי</a> (2020), the Israeli Reform Movement siddur edited by Rabbi Alona Lisitsa (Ph.D.) and Rabbi Dr. Dalia Marx.</p>\n<h3>Source(s)</h3>\n<p><span style=\"float: right;\"><div id=\"attachment_32530\" style=\"width: 170px\" class=\"wp-caption alignleft\"><a href=\"https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/tefilat-ha-adam-Israeli-REform-Movement-2020.jpg\" rel=\"lightbox\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-32530\" src=\"https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/tefilat-ha-adam-Israeli-REform-Movement-2020-160x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"160\" height=\"300\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-32530\" srcset=\"https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/tefilat-ha-adam-Israeli-REform-Movement-2020-160x300.jpg 160w, https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/tefilat-ha-adam-Israeli-REform-Movement-2020.jpg 505w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 160px) 100vw, 160px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-32530\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Tefilat ha-Adam (Israeli Reform Movement, 2020)</p></div></span>  <span style=\"float: left;\"><div id=\"attachment_32658\" style=\"width: 174px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Tefilat-ha-Adam-p.126-127.jpg\" rel=\"lightbox\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-32658\" src=\"https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Tefilat-ha-Adam-p.126-127-164x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"164\" height=\"300\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-32658\" srcset=\"https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Tefilat-ha-Adam-p.126-127-164x300.jpg 164w, https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Tefilat-ha-Adam-p.126-127-560x1024.jpg 560w, https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Tefilat-ha-Adam-p.126-127.jpg 1076w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 164px) 100vw, 164px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-32658\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Tefilat ha-Adam p.126-127</p></div></span><span class=\"\" style=\"display:block;clear:both;height: 0px;border-top-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;\"></span></p>\n",
